{
  "total_duration": 544.057,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 14.136,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象你学了很久英语，终于到了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "London"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，准备开口问路。你说得很认真、很清楚，可是第一个真正的 English speaker 却听不懂你；等他回答时，你又听不懂他。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 14.486,
      "end": 38.829,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Do the English speak English?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“英国人讲的是英语吗？”这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the English"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“英语这门语言”，而是 English people，也就是英格兰人。标题当然不是说英国人不会英语，它是在开一个温和的玩笑：真实世界里的英语，听起来可能和课堂里的英语很不一样。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 39.179,
      "end": 61.459,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课发生在一个 old railway station。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "railway station"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 train station。旧时伦敦的大车站可能很大、很暗，有铁架屋顶、烟雾、行李和很多赶路的人，所以课文说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "big, black and dark"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，不是恐怖，而是又大又陌生。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 61.809,
      "end": 79.425,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有一个词要先懂："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "porter"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。porter 是旧车站里帮旅客搬行李、指路、回答问题的工作人员。今天你可以把他想成 station staff、airport staff、hotel front desk 或 service counter 的人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 79.774,
      "end": 92.914,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这课最重要的不是嘲笑口音，也不是说 British English 很奇怪。它是在告诉你：听不懂真实英语，不代表你没学好，而是你正在从 classroom English 进入 real-world English。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 93.264,
      "end": 113.592,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事一开始，叙述者终于到了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "London"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I arrived in London at last."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是一进 railway station，他就被环境压住了。车站"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was big, black and dark"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，又大又暗，他拖着小行李，心里想：我的 hotel 到底往哪走？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 113.942,
      "end": 131.173,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他决定问一位"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "porter"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I did not know the way to my hotel, so I asked a porter."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他不是乱说，他非常努力："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I not only spoke English very carefully, but very clearly as well."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不但认真，而且清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 131.523,
      "end": 152.563,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是现实很尴尬："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The porter, however, could not understand me."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "叙述者把问题"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "repeated several times"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，重复了好几次，porter 终于懂了。可是 porter 一回答，又轮到叙述者听不懂，因为他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spoke neither slowly nor clearly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 152.913,
      "end": 176.136,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "叙述者解释："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am a foreigner."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "foreigner 是外国人，在这里是中性的说法。porter 放慢了语速，可叙述者还是听不懂，他心里想："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My teacher never spoke English like that!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后两个人看着彼此笑了。porter 说了一句他听懂的话："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "You'll soon learn English!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 176.486,
      "end": 178.046,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "标题为什么好笑？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 178.396,
      "end": 185.065,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为 English people 当然 speak English，可是叙述者觉得他们说的英语和老师说的完全不一样。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 185.415,
      "end": 198.203,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the English"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“英格兰人”，不是“英语”。叙述者真正的问题不是课本学错了，而是真实场景里有 accent、speed、rhythm 和 connected speech。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 198.553,
      "end": 200.982,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那 porter 是不是不友好？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 201.332,
      "end": 216.932,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。课程卡特别提醒我们不要把他演成 rude。他也在努力帮忙。先是没听懂，后来回答太快，最后他放慢，还和叙述者一起笑。这个笑不是嘲笑，是两个人都发现沟通不容易。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 217.282,
      "end": 222.022,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My teacher never spoke English like that"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句为什么重要？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 222.372,
      "end": 233.932,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为老师在课堂里通常会说得慢、清楚、标准。但真实的人在车站、机场、酒店前台说话，会有自己的口音和节奏。第一次听不懂很正常。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 234.282,
      "end": 239.693,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "You'll soon learn English"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是说“你没学过英语”？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 240.043,
      "end": 250.303,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。porter 的意思更像：你会慢慢习惯 real English。你已经会 classroom English，现在要学会真实世界里英语怎么响。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 250.652,
      "end": 253.316,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I arrived in London at last."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 253.666,
      "end": 257.242,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The railway station was big, black and dark."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 257.592,
      "end": 261.696,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I did not know the way to my hotel, so I asked a porter."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 262.046,
      "end": 266.678,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I not only spoke English very carefully, but very clearly as well."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 267.028,
      "end": 270.46,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The porter, however, could not understand me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 270.81,
      "end": 275.106,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I repeated my question several times and at last he understood."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 275.456,
      "end": 279.296,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He answered me, but he spoke neither slowly nor clearly."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 279.646,
      "end": 282.238,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'I am a foreigner,' I said."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 282.587,
      "end": 286.163,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Then he spoke slowly, but I could not understand him."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 286.513,
      "end": 289.801,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My teacher never spoke English like that!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 290.151,
      "end": 293.367,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The porter and I looked at each other and smiled."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 293.717,
      "end": 296.765,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Then he said something and I understood it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 297.115,
      "end": 299.851,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'You'll soon learn English!' he said."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 300.201,
      "end": 301.953,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I wonder."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 302.303,
      "end": 306.071,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In England, each person speaks a different language."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 306.421,
      "end": 310.669,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The English understand each other, but I don't understand them!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 311.018,
      "end": 313.442,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Do they speak English?"
        }
      ]
    },
