      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "porter"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是旧车站里的工作人员，会帮旅客搬行李、指路或回答实际问题。课文里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I asked a porter"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，不是随便问路人，而是问车站 staff。今天的对应场景可以是 airport staff、station staff、hotel front desk 或 service counter。"
        }
      ]
    },
