        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 366.211,
      "end": 381.698,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "wonder"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wonder"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是心里觉得疑惑、在想“到底为什么”。课文最后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I wonder"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，不是随便发呆，而是在想：我能懂老师的英语，为什么到了 England 反而听不懂 English people？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 382.048,
      "end": 405.888,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 是两组配对结构，用来写“两个点同时成立”。第一组是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "not only A, but B as well"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是“不但 A，而且 B”。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I not only spoke English very carefully, but very clearly as well."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他不但 very carefully，而且 very clearly，说明他真的努力了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 406.238,
      "end": 421.573,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二组是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "neither A nor B"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是“既不 A，也不 B”。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he spoke neither slowly nor clearly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。不是 slowly，也不是 clearly，所以叙述者听起来很吃力。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 421.923,
      "end": 439.863,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这两句刚好形成对比：叙述者做了两个 helpful things，carefully 加 clearly；但 porter 的回答少了两个 needed things，not slowly 加 not clearly。语法不是孤立背公式，而是在解释为什么沟通卡住了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 440.213,
      "end": 457.861,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有几个小连接词也要顺手抓住："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "at last"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是终于，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "several times"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是好几次，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "however"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是然而，专门用来把“我说得很清楚”和“他还是不懂”连成一个转折。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 458.21,
      "end": 477.29,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天的车站问路放进你自己的真实生活。你可能在国外的大车站、机场、酒店前台，或地铁服务台，不知道 hotel、platform 或 exit 往哪走。你先礼貌开口，如果对方说得太快，就请他 repeat 或 speak more slowly。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 477.64,
      "end": 498.872,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以照这个顺序说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Excuse me. I don't know the way to my hotel. Could you say that again, please? I am a foreigner. Could you speak more slowly, please? Thank you."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "目标不是说得完美，而是在听不懂的时候还能礼貌地修复沟通。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 499.222,
      "end": 544.057,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课就到这。下面先做 ⓪ 跟读：听课文全文 -> 听原音 -> 录一句 -> 获取反馈，把"
        },
